data.description: Luxury custom home conveniently located between the M Streets and Lakewood! Private oasis backyard with a pool and covered patio! Great drive up appeal, front porch sitting, and professionally landscaped. Quality throughout the home. Grand 2 story entry, featuring a dramatic hardwood staircase. Beautiful gourmet kitchen that opens to the family room. Built in fridge, huge island, commercial grade gas stove and oven. Guest bedroom with an ensuite bath and a study downstairs. Spacious owners suite with a lavish spa like bath. Two nice size bedrooms, Jack and Jill bath, half bath, huge gameroom and a second laundry room upstairs. Recent updates and features: 5 ton HVAC system which covers the downstairs,  Built-in wine cooler, Dishwasher, Exterior Paint, Gutters. Walk to Saint Thomas Aquinas. Minutes to Mockingbird Elementary, White Rock Lake, Northpark Mall, Mockingbird Station, Uptown and more! Back on Market. Buyer's backed out because their job situation changed.
